    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> No need to rebase if it can be merged, no?\n\nIf it can be merged, it can be rebased :). Ideally it would be better to rebase every PR, but this requires to switch back to cli, force push and then accept the pr (there's an issue [about that already](https://github.com/isaacs/github/issues/88)).\n",
